name: Marilyn #1
description:
A modern day AI series of Marilyn Monroe 'screen prints', in homage to the originals by Andy Warhol.

Here I used the exact same photo Warhol used - a publicity photo from the film Niagara. The photo was then synthesised with 'Glitch Art' as the prompt.

Made with Text to Image synthesis (CLIP & VQGan)
